ing. The wind-blown bubble\nscenario requires a single-degenerate progenitor, which should leave behind a\ncompanion star.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Aug 2011 20:15:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
