ddies to interior ventilation and the\nequatorward spreading of Labrador Sea Water are discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Aug 2011 05:43:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 8 Aug 2011 13:30:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-08-09"}
