e sensors to cooperatively position the object and inhibit other irrelevant\n(i.e., farther) sensors from tracking the object. As a result, the\ncommunication and sensing overheads are greatly reduced.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Aug 2011 12:56:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-08-08"}
